The Keiser Report  No. 221
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Saturday, 10 December 2011


[sebaygo1]


Every show Max Keiser looks at all the scandal behind the financial news headlines. This time Max and Stacy discuss central banks and governments 'saving the day' and hostage taking paper silver markets and gold for bonds in Japan. In the second half of the show, Max talks to Satyajit Das, author of Extreme Money, about the European debt crisis.
